{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2944110, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 559318, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "吸收……初中物理", "timestamp": 1636954976, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2944115, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 559318, "reply_to": 2944110, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 再吸收 也是零上", "timestamp": 1636955001, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2944120, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 559318, "reply_to": 2944115, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 下雪时高空温度是零下，不代表地表温度是零下", "timestamp": 1636955046, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2944121, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 559318, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "热传递", "timestamp": 1636955047, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2944124, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 559318, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "？初中物理没学好了属于是。谁告诉你下雪一定是0下化雪一定是0上的", "timestamp": 1636955082, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2944134, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 559318, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你是不是觉得做题的时候假设了稳态，这个世界上就只有稳态了？热传导对流辐射你都当不存在？", "timestamp": 1636955149, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2944136, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 559318, "reply_to": 2944120, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 地上有积雪的话呢", "timestamp": 1636955158, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2944141, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 559318, "reply_to": 2944134, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 积雪算不算稳态？", "timestamp": 1636955184, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2944191, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 559318, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "气温，体感温度，地表温度都是不一样的", "timestamp": 1636955448, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2944203, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 559318, "reply_to": 2944191, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 细说", "timestamp": 1636955529, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2944245, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 559318, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "化雪时融化和升华混合，即使气温低于0度，只要空气干燥，升华也可以继续进行。", "timestamp": 1636955770, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2944258, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 559318, "reply_to": 2944245, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 但是平时人们说的“下雪不冷化雪冷”中的“化”多指融化吧", "timestamp": 1636955849, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2944292, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 559318, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "化雪时需要从周围环境中吸收热量 地表温度变低", "timestamp": 1636956083, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2944298, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 559318, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "😅我就记得初中物理知识 懒得深入探究了", "timestamp": 1636956141, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2944334, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 559318, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "感受一下不就得了，下雪的时候和化雪的哪个冷只要感受过的就知道化雪的时候有多冷，下次下雪记得出门感受一下", "timestamp": 1636956335, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2944382, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 559318, "reply_to": 2944334, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 感受上是这样的 但是感觉违反物理", "timestamp": 1636956837, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2945296, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 559318, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "初中物理给的错误答案：假设0℃，10mm暴雪，融化成水，每平方米吸热3340kJ，可以让其上方100m高的空气柱温度下降26℃（空气密度1.25，定压热容1009）。\n地理和气象学给的正确答案：真实世界不是这样的孤立体系。降雪的条件是冷暖气团交界处，一般情况下是气压高的冷干气团向气压低的暖湿气团移动（冷锋）。降雪后的冷气团取代了降雪前的暖气团，所以气温下降。春天有时会反过来，这时候雪下完了反而更暖和。", "timestamp": 1636963616, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 7, "pid": 559318, "reply": 17, "tag": null, "text": "为什么说“下雪不冷化雪冷”？\n那化雪再冷也是零上，下雪再热也是零下啊", "timestamp": 1636954924, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1636963615, "url": "", "vote": {}}}